lead_paragraph: By the arrival last evening of the Steamship Mexico, Capt Place, we have received Galveston papers to the 19th inst., with corresponding late dates from other portions of the state. The Western Texas states that Capt. Wallace's company of Rangers if to be mustered out of service on the 23d inst.
